
Linux ma compile garna:

Link: version 11 from:
https://libav.org/download.html

Remove purano libav:
apt-get remove libavcodec-dev libavutil-dev


Get libav dependencies:
apt-get build-dep libav-tools

In libav directory from terminal, run configure:
./configure --disable-yasm --disable-static --enable-shared --enable-libx264 --enable-gpl --enable-libvo-aacenc --enable-version3

Build libav:
make

Install libav:
make install
